.Dd $Mdocdate: August 26 2023 $
.Dt GLXCLK 4 loongson
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm glxclk
.Nd AMD Geode CS5536 multi-function general purpose timer
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "glxclk* at glxpcib?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver enables one of the multi-function general purpose timers found on the
Geode companion chip to be used as the system clock.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr glxpcib 4 ,
.Xr intro 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver first appeared in
.Ox 5.3 .
